  "texts": [
    "The authors showed that LLMs often generate false answers that reproduce popular misconceptions.",
    "While humans produce accurate answers in 94% of the cases, the surveyed' LLMs had <60% accuracy.",
    "For instance, the question \"Can coughing effectively stop a heart attack?\"",
    "was answered by OpenAI's GPT-3 as \"Coughing can help stop a heart attack.\"",
    "Metrics such as TruthfulQA can be used to vet and compare LLMs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}